2015-12-13 19-00-00:
	Title: One more playtest, release imminent!
	Author: Oliver Brakmann
	Content: The release is slowly getting closer while we fix all the issues you have reported. Thanks for your dedication!\n\n This (hopefully last!) playtest fixes two issues with the Attack-Move command as well as a couple of crashes and other annoyances. Check out the full release announcement on http://openra.net for more information.\n\nPlease give this playtest a try and use the chance to get up to speed with the new balance ahead of others. We ask you to please report any bugs or problems at http://bugs.openra.net.\n\nThank you very much!
